I was very angry,when i first stood at the wall and started to look for my friends names,were was twitty name,mantecas,chicos,and all the my other guys,I only knew by their nickname,for my life i could not remember their last name or were they were killed or the dates<br>
god!I was so sad not being able to put a name in the wall to any of my friends,Twitty was killed and he was my friend,but we never bother to introduced our selfs,my name was always chico to him,I dont think he knew that my name is Hugo,no matter,I still see your face and remember that stupid yellow monkey of yours<br>
I still miss you and sometimes when im really drunk I cry,see you in heaven.
